# AuditPipe — strict GPT-5.6 forensic audit

AuditPipe performs generic dossier ingestion, GPT-5.6 evidence analysis,
GPT-5.6 dossier synthesis, deterministic verbatim-quote verification, and
model-attested JSON generation. Offline and unattested report generation are
not supported.
